extends layout

block content
  h1= title

  p Welcome to #[em local Library], a very basicExpress web application as a tutorial example on the Mozzilla Developer Network.

  hi Dynamic Content

  if error
    p Error getting dynaamic content
  else
    p The library has the following record counts:


    ul
      li #[strong Books:] !{data.book_count}
      li #[strong Copies:] !{data.book_instance_count}
      li #[strong Copies available:] !{data.book_instance_available}
      li #[strong Authors:] !{data.author_count}
      li #[strong Genres:] !{data.genre_count}